plugins.description:
Plugina konfigureren. Bija plugin-luohkáid dahje objeavtta mii lea čállojuvvon plugin-namain.
```js
import plugins, { image, link, table } from 'suneditor/src/plugins';
{ plugins: plugins,
plugins: [image, link, table],
plugins: { image, link, table }
}
```

allowedEmptyTags.description:
Listu merkemiin maid sáhttá doallat vaikko daid árvvut leat guoros.
- Default čuovvu {@link DEFAULTS.ALLOWED_EMPTY_NODE_LIST}
- `ALLOWED_EMPTY_NODE_LIST` čatnon oktii vai šaddá loahpalaš `allowedEmptyTags`-listtu.

attributeWhitelist.description:
Deattuha lassi iešvuođaid mat dohkkehit juohke mearkka. `"*"` guoská buot mearkkaide.
- Dás meroštallojuvvon njuolggadusat ovttastuvvojit {@link PrivateBaseOptions.__defaultAttributeWhitelist}:ii.
```js
{
attributeWhitelist: {
a: 'href|target',
img: 'src|alt',
'*': 'id|data-*'
}
}
```

convertTextTags.description:
Kárte teakstastiillaid dihto HTML-mearkkaide.
```js
{
convertTextTags: {
bold: 'b',
italic: 'i',
underline: 'u',
strike: 's'
}
}
```

tagStyles.description:
Deattuha dohkkehuvvon stiillaid HTML-mearkkaide. Nubbi lea merkejuvvon namma(t), árvu lea johtolatráddjejuvvon dohkkehuvvon stiillat.
```js
{
tagStyles: {
'table|td': 'border|color|background-color',
hr: 'border-top'
}
}
```

shortcuts.description:
Eaktodáhtolaš tastaturčujuhusat.
- Nuppit mat álget `_` leat geavaheaddji mearridan iešheanalaš čujuhusat. Juohke árvu lea `[keyCombo, hintLabel]` ​​páraid ráidu.
- Nuppiid kombinašuvnnat geavahit `c` (Ctrl/Cmd), `s` (Shift) ja `KeyEvent.code` árvvuid mat leat ovttastuvvon `+`:in.
- Geavat `$~pluginName.method` go galggat gohččut dihto plugin-vuogádaga.
```js
{
shortcuts: {
bold: ['c+KeyB', 'B'],
_h1: ['c+s+Digit1+$~blockStyle.applyHeaderByShortcut', '']
}
}
```

externalLibs.description:
Olggobeale girjerádjosat nugo CodeMirror, KaTeX dahje MathJax.
- Geahča {@link https://github.com/ARA-developer/suneditor/blob/develop/guide/external-libraries.md External Libraries Guide}
```js
{
externalLibs: {
katex: window.katex,
codeMirror: { src: CodeMirror }
}
}
```

allowedExtraTags.description:
Deattuha lassi dohkkehuvvon dahje ii dohkkehuvvon merkemiid. `true` dohkkehit, `false` ​​ii dohkkehit.
- Standárda čuovvu {@link DEFAULTS.EXTRA_TAG_MAP}
```js
{
allowedExtraTags: {
script: false,
style: false,
mark: true
}
}
```

events.description:
Geavaheaddji dáhpáhusaid gieđahalli konfigurašuvdna.
```js
{
events: {
onChange: (content) => console.log(content),
onImageUploadBefore: (files, info) => true
}
}
```
